Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.99,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:113030,114990}Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:113488,115198}I wonder if Mitamura-kun will be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.57,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:115198,117576}Nobody will show up.\NIt's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.28,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:117576,119286}So what if it's Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.28,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:119286,121288}They'll all be there to welcome us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.12,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:121288,124124}I think so, too.\NAfter all, we have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:06.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:124124,126877}Maybe the whole school\Nis coming to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.33,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:126877,130339}But you care only about\NMitamura-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:14.59,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:132424,134593}It's okay if there's no one\Nto welcome us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:18.47,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:134593,138471}What matters most is that we know\Nwe did our best ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.93,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:138471,139931}– Don't you think so, Ayuhara-san?\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:22.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:139931,142934}Oh, look.\NWe're already so close to Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:142934,144936}Come on, girls.\NLet's get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.78,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:157449,158784}Let's see, let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.95,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:160243,161953}No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.58,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:161953,163580}What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:163580,165248}That's strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.08,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:165248,168085}I don't believe not a single person\Ncame to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.63,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:169127,171630}What are you doing?\NExit is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.88,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:171630,173882}Yes, yes.\NWe're going, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.84,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:176885,178845}Gates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:23.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:201159,203078}I think our parents\Nare outside, Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:203078,205580}That's where Mitamura-kun\Nmust be waiting for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.29,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:209543,212295}{\fad(0,1000)}Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.13,Alternative,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:211920,213130}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:44.30,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:218969,224307}{\fad(0,2000)}Congratulations on your victory!{NOTE:祝優勝}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.63,0:03:48.89,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:222639,228895}{\fad(2000,0)}Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:231440,234276}We have fought hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:59.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:234276,239363}We wanted to have nothing to be ashamed of\Nwhen we look back in five or ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:239363,240907}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:05.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:240907,245287}Honestly, we weren't thinking of anything grand\Nsuch as winning for our school or for the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:08.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:245287,248457}And yet you've all come here\Nto celebrate our victory with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:248457,249833}I'm not sure if we deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.83,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:249833,250834}Of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:11.66,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:250834,251667}He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.46,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:251667,252461}You're our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.46,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:252461,254463}I love you, Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:260385,263513}I'm sorry for you,\Nbut the only thing I love is volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.01,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:265307,267017}Rejected, rejected.{NOTE:振られてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.53,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:281990,283533}Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:47.37,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:283533,287370}It is honorable that your girls are so modest,\Nbut I think sometimes they are too modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.95,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:287370,288955}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.41,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:288955,292417}I think they deserve a bit of rest\Nafter so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:56.63,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:292417,296630}Of course, I do not want\Nto criticize your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:296630,299549}Oh, no, by no means.\NThat's a great advice, Mr. Headmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:02.34,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:299549,302344}I've already told them to rest\Nduring the Golden Week…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:302344,304387}…and let themselves forget\Nabout volleyball for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.43,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:304387,305430}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.76,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:305430,307766}Makimura proposed a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.10,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:307766,310101}That's a great idea.\NGood, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.10,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:311269,313104}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.06,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{TIME:314064,316066}Now I understand why they won.\NGood, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.03,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:323198,326034}"Many are the hills,\Nthe mountains of Yamato.{NOTE:大和には郡山あれどとりよろふ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.41,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:326034,328411}Yet when I ascend heavenly Kaguyama,\Nthe peerless mountain…{NOTE:天の香具山登り立ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.83,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:328411,331832}…when I look down on the land, where the land\Nstretches, hearth smoke rises everywhere.{NOTE:国見をすれば国原は煙立つ立つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.00,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:331832,334000}Where the water stretches,\Nwater birds fly everywhere.{NOTE:海原は鷗立つ立つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.46,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:334000,337462}Ah, a splendid country,\Nthis land Yamato of bounteous harvests!"{NOTE:うまし国そ蜻蛉島大和の国は}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.00,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:338421,342008}I think I have read it somewhere.\NWhat was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:342008,343260}Kojiki, right?{NOTE:古事記}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:47.01,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:342008,347013}Kojiki – the oldest extant chronicle in Japan\NMan'yōshū – earliest Japanese poetry anthology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.26,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:343260,345262}It's Man'yōshū.\NEmperor Jomei.{NOTE:万葉集舒明天皇}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.30,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:345262,347305}Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:348306,349558}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.97,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:349558,350976}– Yeah.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.57,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:361194,362571}A deer!\NHah, a deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.57,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:362571,363572}You're such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.57,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:365490,367576}Ah! You have to wait\Nfor your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.29,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:375584,377294}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.21,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:378378,379212}Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.09,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:382048,383091}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.42,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:384008,386428}Why the heck are you\Nscaring off poor animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.47,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:386428,387470}Poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.38,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:387470,389389}They're pretty sly, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.39,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:389389,391391}Sly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.10,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:391391,393101}They're weak,\Nso they beg for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.98,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:393101,396980}Those beasts approach only to take food,\Nnot because they like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:40.06,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:396980,400066}I can't stand parasites like them.\NThey don't deserve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.98,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:400066,403986}But I have even less sympathy\Nfor those who let themselves get duped like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.40,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:403986,405405}Hey!\NWait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.82,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:410118,411828}You're worse than the fawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.78,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:411828,413788}I scared you with nothing.\NCoward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.62,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:413788,415624}Coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.75,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:415624,417751}You messed with the wrong person, gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.42,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:417751,420420}My name is Ishimatsu.\NI'll make you not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.42,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:420420,421421}Ishimatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.84,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:421421,424841}I've got to tell you, Ishimatsu,\Nyou've got one hell of an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.76,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:426551,427760}Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.93,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:433725,435936}You're ugly, but strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.97,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:435936,438979}Do you play volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.85,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:438979,441858}Volleyball?\NSo, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:24.27,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:441858,444277}I'm a regular player\Nin the Fujimi High School team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.69,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:444277,446695}Huh, the number one\Nhigh school in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.11,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:446695,449115}So, what difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.74,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:449115,450742}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:35.83,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:450742,455830}I may hate begging fawns,\Nbut I hate weak posers like you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.08,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:455830,458083}Are you trying to make me mad?\NIt's working well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:458083,460710}Ishimatsu, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.29,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:461169,463296}Ah, I think I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.21,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:463296,465215}It was Ayuhara just now, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.92,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:465215,467926}Hey, watch you honorifics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.51,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:467926,469511}I have no respect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.76,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:469511,472763}Just look at her big eyes and round face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:57.68,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:472763,477686}She'd be better off dancing\Nrather than playing volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.10,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:480605,482107}Oh, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.19,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:482107,484192}Goodbye, Ishimatsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:492409,494369}Who was it just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.78,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:494369,495787}Never mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.62,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:495787,497622}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.46,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:508842,510468}Outta my way,\Noutta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.56,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:523565,526568}I've heard that only about one\Nin thousand deer hates people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.94,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:526568,527944}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.50,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:540749,542500}You should have a bit more courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.33,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:542500,545336}But it's not like\Nyou guys live long, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:37.16,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:571696,577160}She made fun of us, but what's more,\Nshe tortured innocent deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.62,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:577160,578620}I can't quite imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.20,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:578620,581206}Shut up!\NDon't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:45.04,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:581206,585043}Ishimatsu, calm down. We could afford\Nthis hotel thanks to Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.75,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:585043,587754}If we keep yelling,\Nthey'll drive us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.09,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:588421,591091}Alright, alright.\NBut wait, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.26,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:591091,594260}She said that in her opinion it's absurd\Nthat we're number one in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.76,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:594260,595762}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.59,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:595762,598598}Word for word,\N"I hate weak posers like you".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.43,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:598598,600433}Wow, she said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.93,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:600433,603937}Then she started\Nto talk trash about Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.02,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:603937,606021}Rather than playing ball,\Nshe should play on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.89,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:606021,606898}That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.90,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:606898,609901}And you just stood there\Nletting her talk all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.36,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:609901,612362}I won't forgive her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.61,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:612362,615615}Yeah! Let us know\Nnext time you see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.70,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:616825,619702}I'll cut her to pieces for Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:23.74,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:619702,623748}Oh, no! Is this how\NYamato girls behave at the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:624749,626251}They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:626251,629712}They got full, so they went\Nto play some table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:629712,631339}We spent a little too much today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:631339,634217}Don't worry, we'll economize tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:636427,637720}The moon's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:637720,639013}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:44.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:639013,644477}"On the horizon – isn't that the same moon\Nthat rises in spring over the Hill of Mikasa?"{NOTE:あまの原ふりさけみれば春日なる三笠の山にいでし月かも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:43.64,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:639013,643643}A poem by Abe no Nakamaro\N(Kokin Wakashū 9:406)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:649816,651276}It's so beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:653444,654737}Especially at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:656281,657448}It's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:658908,661035}Ah, it's those bikers again!
Comment: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:32.31,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:692317,692317}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.56,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:726643,729562}Left: Uguisu Falls\NRight: Takisaka Walking Path
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.83,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:754170,756839}Ishimatsu, are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.50,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:756839,759509}Everyone went ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.34,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:759509,763346}What's taking you so long?\NHow much more are you going to drink that water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.80,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:763346,764806}I'm going, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.55,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:764806,767558}She doesn't get how great\Nthis water is. Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.56,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:767976,769560}I'm going without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.36,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:780738,782365}Takeichi-san, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.91,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:782365,785910}Hurry up or\NI'll go without you for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.53,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:787120,789539}Your stomach will hurt,\NIshimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:13.29,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:789539,793293}Oh, come on. It was clear,\Njust like drinking water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.13,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:801884,803136}Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:803136,804262}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.55,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:804262,806556}Oh, I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.89,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:806556,809892}How much further do we till\NYagyū Kaidō?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:33.06,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:809892,813062}I'd say we're halfway there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.77,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:813062,814772}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:815732,817859}Let's wait for Ishimatsu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.27,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:817859,820278}Yeah. Maybe they've stopped, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.82,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:820278,821821}Man, they're moving fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.82,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:821821,823823}Hurry up and you'll rest\Nas long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.49,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:824699,826492}They're sure taking their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.45,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:826492,827452}Look, they're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.12,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:829620,832123}Oh, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:56.87,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:835918,836877}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.29,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:836877,838295}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.25,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:838295,839255}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.46,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:839255,840464}We're going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.42,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:840464,842425}Not even a little pause?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.59,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:842425,845595}From now on it'll be even more scenic.\NYou'll be enchanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:10.47,Sign,(note),0,0,0,,{TIME:845595,850475}Various religious structures made of stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.76,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:845595,847764}First an okagetōrō,\Nthen a kasajizō.{NOTE:おかげ灯篭。笠地蔵。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.47,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:847764,850475}After we pass through the forest,\Nit's a gorintō.{NOTE:五輪の塔}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:14.14,Sign,(note),0,0,0,,{TIME:850475,854145}A large temple in Nara Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:14.14,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:850475,854145}Then after we pass it,\Nit's one of the National Treasures, Enjō-ji.{NOTE:国宝　円成寺}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.85,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:854145,855855}I don't think I'm gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.10,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:855855,858107}She's like a walking history book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:858107,861819}You don't have to take history classes\Nto enjoy the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:26.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:861819,866282}But it's nice to focus on something other than\Nreceptions, blocks and attacks once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.74,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:867450,870745}You're one to talk.\NWhat is that ball doing on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:871537,874874}Professor Hongou told us to forget\Nabout volleyball for a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:874874,877085}And here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:39.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:877085,879003}I'm sorry, I'm sorry.\NIt was out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:879003,882256}I feel kind of lonely and insecure\Nif I don't have one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:882256,884592}Kozue, you're a real\Nvolleyball freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.07,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:907865,910076}Oh? This time it's Makimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.99,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:910076,912995}Makimura-san, we'll be going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.74,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:912995,915748}Sure.\NI'll catch up to you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.10,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:936269,937103}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.02,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:937103,938020}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.10,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:938020,939104}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.48,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:943359,944485}Are you okay, Tobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.78,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:947196,948781}Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.24,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:948781,951242}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:54.07,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:951242,954078}Damn, that was close.\NYou hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.78,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:954078,956789}I'm unscathed,\Nbut the lamp doesn't seem to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.33,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:959208,963337}You've got to be kidding.\NWe can't drive in the dark anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.71,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:963921,965715}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.63,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:966966,969635}Really, girl.\NSorry won't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.30,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:969635,972305}Do you have money\Nto pay for the repairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.47,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:972305,975475}Yes. Uhm…\NBut I have to return to hotel first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.80,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:975475,976809}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.39,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:976809,979395}It's a guest house\Nnear Shin'yakushiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.19,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:980271,982190}It's in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.77,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:982190,984775}Too bad.\NYou're with friends, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:28.36,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:984775,988362}Talk to them and let them\Ncome up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.40,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:988362,989405}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.61,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:989405,991616}We'll be waiting at Enjō-ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.45,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:991616,993451}I'll keep this as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.86,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:993451,994869}Let's go, Tobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.37,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:994869,996370}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.84,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014555,1015848}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.43,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015848,1019435}Don't they have better places\Nto drive through?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:04.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022103,1024106}Oh?\NIt's Makimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029403,1030655}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.12,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037411,1039120}Don't you worry, Makimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039120,1042458}When it comes to money,\NI can always ask my Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.41,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043584,1045419}Come on,\Nthere's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.54,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045419,1048548}They're the ones\Nwho have to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048548,1051133}But how do we make them\Nreturn the sketchbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.63,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051133,1053636}I'm sorry to give you\Nall the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.55,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053636,1055555}It's just a sketchbook.\NThey can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.26,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055555,1057265}That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.10,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057265,1060101}All you promised them\Nwas to go to Enjō-ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.22,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060101,1063229}Yep. We'll go to Enjō-ji.\NThen we'll kick their asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.14,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063229,1064146}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.81,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064146,1065815}So, you want to solve it\Nwith a brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.90,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065815,1067900}Now, now.\NLet's not be so direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.36,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067900,1069360}Kozue, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069360,1071821}For now let's just go to Enjō-ji.\NThen we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:56.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071821,1076909}Maybe they threw a false accusation.\NBut what if they didn't? We'd better not run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.49,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076909,1078494}Captain,\Nsometimes you're too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082707,1085167}Forehead, how much\Ndo you know about engines?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.87,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085167,1087878}Engines? Ah, well,\NI know a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:18.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097430,1098889}Wow, it's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.82,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115281,1116824}So you came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.28,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119535,1121287}Do you have the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121287,1123080}Yes, we'll give it in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.70,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123080,1125708}Oh, that's great.\NTake your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:54.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130129,1134258}Ah, it's you who fell, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.71,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134258,1135718}Hm?\NYes. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137553,1139764}Oh my goodness!\NYou're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.93,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139764,1140931}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.89,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140931,1142892}You must've injured yourself\Nwhen you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:06.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142892,1146228}Don't move around much.\NI'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.52,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146228,1148522}I'm sure I'd feel something, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.31,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149774,1151317}What a cool machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.31,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151317,1153319}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.40,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153319,1156405}"Mighty Six".\NIt's the symbol of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.07,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156405,1159075}Whoa, even cooler stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:23.49,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159075,1163495}What does it refer to?\NIt sounds pretty rad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.24,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163495,1165247}Hey, it works fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.83,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167208,1168834}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.29,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168834,1170294}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:34.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170836,1174256}I'm glad it's working again.\NWell then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.80,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176509,1177802}Hey! W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180012,1181097}As if I'd listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.26,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181764,1183265}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.18,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184266,1185184}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.77,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190690,1193776}Grab me once again,\Nand I'll show you my "falling leaf".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.65,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194151,1195653}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.32,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199156,1201325}Damn it to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.03,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201325,1203035}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.70,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206872,1208708}How was it?\NNow you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:12.12,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208708,1212128}Tobe, Tani.\NYou can't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.17,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216924,1219176}You were absolutely right, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.59,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219176,1222596}I'm convinced these girls will be\Nworthy opponents for our Mighty Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.82,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244118,1246829}Waking up so early really gets to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:51.95,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246829,1251959}I know it's bad to sleep for too long,\Nbut man, I'll need a day outta my life after that trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.64,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267516,1269643}He looks strong, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:14.35,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272146,1274356}I love Buddha\Nwhen he makes such a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.23,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274356,1275232}It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.52,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275232,1276525}I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.73,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276525,1277735}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.32,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277735,1279320}Anybody from your group would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:21.48,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279320,1281489}But it'll be easier\Nif it's you, Ishimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.69,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281489,1282698}Wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.57,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282698,1283573}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.41,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285451,1287411}Well, I see you're still angry,\Nare you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:30.74,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287411,1290748}You're offended because I dared\Nto criticize your team and your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.50,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290748,1292500}Don't start with this trash again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.92,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292500,1295920}See? You're threatening me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.79,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295920,1298798}Stop being so impudent\Nor I'll make you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.13,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298798,1300131}Impudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:45.84,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300131,1305846}Oh, is that how you see me? Then what if I say\Nthat Ayuhara is a weakling and a show-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.64,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306847,1308641}You've asked for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.01,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308641,1310017}Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:53.43,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310017,1313437}If you want to fight me this bad,\NI'll take you to just the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.23,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313437,1316232}How does that sound?\NOr maybe you chicken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.81,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316232,1318818}Ha! It's you who should be chickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.52,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318818,1320528}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.82,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320528,1321821}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:13.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332164,1333457}Have you seen Ishimatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.75,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333457,1336752}No, I thought she's here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337418,1340714}Not even a trace of her.\NWhere could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340714,1342550}I'll look for her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.51,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347805,1349515}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:38.18,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357189,1358189}We're sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:40.94,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359692,1360943}You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:43.19,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360943,1363195}You said we'd fight one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:44.61,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363195,1364612}I never said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:46.78,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364612,1366782}One-on-one fights are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.28,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366782,1369285}I was thinking more\Nabout a six-on-six fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.16,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1372162}Why don't you\Nintroduce yourselves to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.91,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376208,1377918}Me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:22:59.25,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377918,1379253}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:01.17,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1379253,1381171}I'm a former tennis champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:02.63,Default,Tani,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381171,1382631}You'd better take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:06.63,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384133,1386635}I'm Tobe.\NI have fourth dan in jūdō.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:09.51,Default,Kamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1386635,1389513}Kamura.\NI'm a soccer goalkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:12.14,Default,Kasagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389513,1392141}Kasagi. I'm a boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.98,Default,Tamiya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396353,1399982}My name is Tamiya and I have won\Nthe national championship in wrestling twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:22.35,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399982,1402359}That leaves me.\NI play volleyball a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:25.73,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1403611,1405738}The six of us\Nare the Mighty Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:26.78,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405738,1406780}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.86,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1406780,1408866}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.78,Default,Tobe,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408866,1410783}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:37.16,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412745,1417166}We challenge Fujimi High School,\Nthe number one team in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422171,1424423}Ishimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:46.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424423,1426842}Ishimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:50.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427843,1430512}Ishimatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:52.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1430679,1432514}Ishimatsu…
Comment: 0,0:23:59.43,0:23:59.43,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1439437,1439437}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:08.44,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443359,1448447}Ishimatsu takes the The Mighty Six' challenge\Nall by herself and receives severe beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:11.40,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448447,1451408}Kozue watches wounded\NIshimatsu in terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.32,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1451408,1454328}She wants to avoid pointless fights\Nand unnecessary conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:18.95,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454328,1458958}But the Mighty Six's continued taunting\Nput her patience to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:23.67,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1458958,1463671}Finally she's pushed over the edge when Maya\Nstarts to drive her bike in a blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:26.54,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463671,1466548}Please look forward to the next episode.
